果網上報稅過左期經網上報係咪一定斷正?</blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"569cf54d0116a77aec0a3752017aa1312088593b","tid":313751,"uid":44298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:25:45.000Z","msg":"冇寄信黎會唔會老闆冇報？"},{"pid":"31e54d1a0803578393f462211c6d7aa42d16e2f0","tid":313751,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:36:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔厄你<br />\n試過無交稅單<br />\n寄左封信黎話罰10萬</blockquote><br />\n無交稅表點會一開波就10萬？你係唔係漏報入息定係稅局加徵罰款呀？<br />\n利得稅通常初犯就會$1,200，屢犯$3,000都見過。"},{"pid":"29dc49bd30295c50ae27b8496c917dadffc0d0d1","tid":313751,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>順便問下，15年尾開始返ft<br />\n到依家都未收過稅局既信，是否正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？</blockquote><br />\n你望下你張56B，佢填你幾多人工？<br />\n如果你人工唔過<span style=\"color: red;\">個人</span>免稅額，收唔到正常。<br />\n有D公司唔理過唔過免稅額都報。<br />\n如果你係個，稅局網頁有表格下載，通知佢發出稅表。<br />\n我呢D入息過個人，計埋父母唔過，仲年年要我填。心諗稅局係唔係好得閒。"},{"pid":"f92ed75d2338d885908b26843145a3467520fe39","tid":313751,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:38:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1200<br />\n出完1200罰單都唔報就估你稅</blockquote><br />\n咁能多?<br />\n<br />\n如果網上報稅過左期經網上報係咪一定斷正?</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote>"},{"pid":"48415975f33f36645671874e8f636031e0ad7128","tid":313751,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T13:59:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>1200<br />\n出完1200罰單都唔報就估你稅</blockquote><br />\n咁能多?<br />\n<br />\n如果網上報稅過左期經網上報係咪一定斷正?</blockquote></blockquote></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n薪俸稅初犯一般罰$600。<br />\n如果仲未報嘅，趁佢未出reminder或者罰款通知書時好快手報啦！<br />\n一收到你就要諗方法求情啦！"},{"pid":"1c889236250e20eba0a90692e3bc626ba4908fc5","tid":313751,"uid":103237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-09T14:01:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>